\begin_layout Subsection
Apple Macintosh OS X
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Salstat2 should work on almost any version of OS X on a 32 or 64 bit Intel
 based Mac.
 We have not tried it on previous PowerPC based Macs, although it may work
 if you ran it from source and built dependencies yourself.
 If you manage to do this, let us know (and send installation instructions
 and images!)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
At present, only a portable version of the OS X App bundle is created.
 As such, you should not have to worry about installing any dependencies.
 Even if you have versions of dependencies already on your machine, the
 versions within the portable bundle will be used.
 We don't have any immediate plans to produce a non-portable version (since
 nobody has asked.)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
